Assumtions
==========

You have at least followed and succeeded the Hello, World tutorial
at http://developer.android.com/resources/tutorials/hello-world.html

Currently Game Of Life expects sdk and virtual machine for at least android 3.2

Dependencies
============
This program depends on the excelent file chooser by Paul Burke (Apache License 2.0)
at https://github.com/iPaulPro/aFileChooser

Setup instructions
==================

$ cd tmp
$ git clone git@github.com:ppareit/GameOfLife.git

Start Eclipse
File -> New -> Project
Choose Android/Android project
Click Next
Create project from existing source
Browse to location /home/ppareit/tmp/GameOfLife
Click Finish

Browse to one of the java sourcefiles
CTRL+F11 (Run) and select 'Android Application'


Happy hacking!
